    {
      "id": "sec_why",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "layout": "boxed",
        "content_width": {"size": 1260, "unit": "px"},
        "gap": "no",
        "padding": {"top": "90", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "unit": "px", "isLinked": false},
        "css_classes": "prt-gap-127"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "col_why_left",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {"_column_size": 49},
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "w_why_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "\u00bfPor qu\u00e9 elegirnos?",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "left",
                "title_color": "#000000",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "typography_font_weight": "600",
                "typography_font_size": {"size": 26, "unit": "px"},
                "typography_line_height": {"size": 31.2, "unit": "px"}
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "w_why_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p><strong>Somos un partner visual.</strong> Sostenemos tu identidad y cuidamos cada imagen como parte de un todo.</p><p>La <strong>imagen</strong> no se delega sin m\u00e1s: se acompa\u00f1a. Trabajamos desde una visi\u00f3n compartida para que cada entrega mantenga coherencia, calidad y nivel.</p><p>Variedad de <strong>retoques</strong>. Eficiencia real en el flujo de trabajo. Rentabilidad sin perder calidad. <strong>Generaci\u00f3n de im\u00e1genes con IA</strong> e IA aplicada al marketing para optimizar procesos.</p><p>Compromiso real en plazos exigentes. <strong>Nuestro objetivo es claro:</strong> que destaques frente a la competencia y que tu imagen siempre est\u00e9 a la altura.</p>",
                "text_color": "#000000",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "typography_font_weight": "400",
                "typography_font_size": {"size": 16, "unit": "px"},
                "typography_line_height": {"size": 19.2, "unit": "px"}
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "w_why_btn",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Proyectos Recientes",
                "link": {"url": "#", "is_external": false, "nofollow": false},
                "align": "left",
                "background_color": "#FFFFFF",
                "button_text_color": "#000000",
                "border_border": "solid",
                "border_width": {"top": "1", "right": "1", "bottom": "1", "left": "1", "unit": "px", "isLinked": true},
                "border_color": "#000000",
                "border_radius": {"top": "8", "right": "8", "bottom": "8", "left": "8", "unit": "px", "isLinked": true},
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "typography_font_weight": "500",
                "typography_font_size": {"size": 16, "unit": "px"},
                "button_background_hover_color": "#000000",
                "hover_color": "#FFFFFF"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "col_why_right",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {"_column_size": 51},
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "w_accordion",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "accordion",
              "settings": {
                "tabs": [
                  {
                    "_id": "acc_01",
                    "tab_title": "01 \u2014 EXPERIENCIA",
                    "tab_content": "Retoque de im\u00e1genes para marcas exigentes que quieren que el retoque sea una parte estrat\u00e9gica del proceso."
                  },
                  {
                    "_id": "acc_02",
                    "tab_title": "02 \u2014 CALIDAD",
                    "tab_content": "Est\u00e1ndares de calidad que garantizan resultados impecables en cada proyecto."
                  },
                  {
                    "_id": "acc_03",
                    "tab_title": "03 \u2014 TECNOLOG\u00cdA",
                    "tab_content": "Herramientas de \u00faltima generaci\u00f3n combinadas con IA para resultados superiores."
                  },
                  {
                    "_id": "acc_04",
                    "tab_title": "04 \u2014 COMPROMISO",
                    "tab_content": "Compromiso total con los plazos de entrega y la satisfacci\u00f3n del cliente."
                  }
                ],
                "selected_icon": {"value": "fas fa-plus", "library": "fa-solid"},
                "selected_active_icon": {"value": "fas fa-minus", "library": "fa-solid"},
                "title_color": "#000000",
                "title_background": "#FFFFFF",
                "tab_active_color": "#000000",
                "title_typography_typography": "custom",
                "title_typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "title_typography_font_weight": "600",
                "title_typography_font_size": {"size": 16, "unit": "px"},
                "content_color": "#000000",
                "content_typography_typography": "custom",
                "content_typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "content_typography_font_weight": "400",
                "content_typography_font_size": {"size": 16, "unit": "px"},
                "border_color": "#000000"
